VALUES('Air Foamposite Pro', 'Nike', 'Color Shift', 230, 'Become a pro at the sneaker game and cop the Air Foamposite Pro Color Shift. This Air Foamposite Pro comes with a dirty rose gold upper, black Nike “Swoosh”, black midsole, and a black sole. These sneakers released in April 2019 and retailed for $230.', 2019, 'https://sneakerbardetroit.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Nike-Air-Foamposite-Pro-Hyper-Crimson-Black-624041-800-Release-Date-4.jpg','https://sneakerbardetroit.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Nike-Air-Foamposite-Pro-Hyper-Crimson-Black-624041-800-Release-Date-2-1.jpg', 'https://sneakerbardetroit.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Nike-Air-Foamposite-Pro-Hyper-Crimson-Black-624041-800-Release-Date-Price-4.jpg', 'https://sneakerbardetroit.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Nike-Air-Foamposite-Pro-Hyper-Crimson-Black-624041-800-Release-Date-Price-5.jpg');

VALUES('Nike Air Max 270 Doernbecher', 'Nike', 'Black/Metallic Gold-Medium Olive', 150, 'Blend in with the deep pits of the sneaker world while rocking the Air Max 270 Doernbecher (2018). This Air Max 270 comes with an army fatigue upper, gold Nike “Swoosh”, black midsole with gold accents, and a black sole. These sneakers released in December 2018 and retailed for $150.', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Images/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546756036&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Images/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Lv2/img31.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546756036&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Images/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Lv2/img21.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546756036&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Images/Nike-Air-Max-270-Doernbecher-2018/Lv2/img10.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546756036&w=1300');

VALUES('Nike Epic React Flyknit', 'Nike', 'Wolf-Grey/White-Cool Grey-Pure Platinum', 150, 'Take your everyday training session or casual day to epic new heights in the Women''s Nike Epic React Flyknit Running Shoes.', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Images/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Images/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Images/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Images/Nike-Epic-React-Flyknit-Wolf-Grey/Lv2/img08.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200');

VALUES('Nike Kyrie V Concepts Ikhet', 'Nike', 'Multi-Color', 180, 'This Nike Kyrie 5 is inspired by Kyrie’s Hamsa hand tattoo. Its Sandy Beige upper nods to the age of Ancient Egypt and pyramids, while having a chiseled Grey Swoosh, Red tongue to represent the nose of the Sphinx before it decayed, atop a Purple sole that represents the sunset against the pyramids. Dual branding on the tongue shroud, along with Egyptian hieroglyphs on each heel completes the design.', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Images/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546094117&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Images/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546094117&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Images/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Lv2/img18.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546094117&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Images/Nike-Kyrie-5-Concepts-Ikhet-Special-Box/Lv2/img10.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546094117&w=1300');

